Installation

1. Run migrate.py to prepare the database
2. Run run.py to launch the server
3. Open your browser, navigate to 127.0.0.1:5000
3a. Run TamperMonkey Script (tampermonkey.js) on your target StepStone Page, result will be copied to your clipboard.
4. Switch to the Tab "NEUE STELLE" and paste the result of the stepstone page to the blank and hit Enter
5. Enjoy